 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"the air\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It led to her pulling out of four individual finals at a Games where she had been tipped for several gold medals.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four individual finals\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"a Games\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"several gold medals\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She returned to compete in the beam final, taking an emotional bronze, but it was not until now - eight years after she won four gold medals at Rio 2016 - that she could return to the top of the Olympic podium.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1794, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beam final\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1625}, {\"ngram\": \"an emotional bronze\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"four gold medals\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic podium\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now that I am much older, we have so much more experience and we are out here really having fun and enjoying what we are doing - so I think it's just different,\\\" she said when asked about the 2016 and 2024 team golds.\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much more experience\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 and 2024 team golds\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has qualified for another four finals in Paris, with her next medal opportunity coming in Thursday's all-around final.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2063, \"end\": 2068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.289639912989428e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"another four finals\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"her next medal opportunity\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday's all-around final\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This video can not be played Paris 2024 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 USA gymnasts Simone Biles and Jordan Chiles react to gold medal After the events in Tokyo, it had looked like we might have seen Biles at her final Olympics.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2200, \"end\": 2212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 2217, \"end\": 2230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 2272, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999996359852711, \"rank\": 3.640130537522518e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This video\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2152}, {\"ngram\": \"USA gymnasts\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2198}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medal\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"her final Olympics\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, you are not going draw a celebrity crowd and transcend your sport unless you really are something special.\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a celebrity crowd\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"your sport\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When she returned to gymnastics last summer after a two-year break, it was soon clear that she was still at her best.\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"a two-year break\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, you could argue, even better.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had soon won a sixth world all-around title and showcased some of her most difficult gymnastics, and she had also added a new skill, the Biles II vault - a fifth move to be named after her.\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sixth world\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"all-around title\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"her most difficult gymnastics\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"a new skill\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"the Biles II vault\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"a fifth move\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even coming into these Olympics she submitted a new uneven bars move to the gymnastics federation, meaning she will become the only active gymnast to have eponymous skills on all four apparatus if she performs it here.\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2893, \"end\": 2903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gymnastics_at_the_2016_Summe