 {\"sentence\": \"She has given a detailed account in a recent Netflix documentary about what happened in Tokyo, the pressure of expectation and the impact of being called a \\\"quitter\\\" by some on social media and beyond at the time.\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3332, \"end\": 3339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5158137581957374e-16, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}, {\"begin\": 3375, \"end\": 3380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999996359852711, \"rank\": 3.640130537522518e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a detailed account\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3319}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"expectation\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"quitter\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3476}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When speaking at a hearing into the Larry Nassar abuse scandal she said the \\\"scars of this horrific abuse\\\" by the former USA team doctor had been an \\\"exceptionally difficult burden\\\" without her family at the pandemic-hit Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3538, \"end\": 3550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"score\": 0.9517961037151659, \"rank\": 0.05064519186039055, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_ab